{
  "stem": "4272.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were, later on, together and we went through camps together and the ghettos together and all that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How did you feel when the Germans came into Poland?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Truthfully, if I didn't know what went on with the Jews that they sent back to Poland, I wouldn't know what to expect, because-- but-- but this was so real that we were all scared, and we were talking about it.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were afraid that the young men should run away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They should go to Russia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know that the old people and the children and the girls were in just as much, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, danger as the young men were.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When did laws against the Jews start?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Almost immediately.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Almost immediately.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I came home-- they formed the ghetto in 19-- the end of 1940, I think.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I lost my train of thought.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What was the question?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were-- I was asking you about [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when things started to--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Happen to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, almost-- almost immediately.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was walking-- I remember one incident, I was walking the street with my younger sister on the sidewalk, and a German came towards us and he stopped us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, wo gehst du?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where are you going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, I live here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he looked at us-- we were both blond and blue eyes, and they couldn't stand it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he took another look at us, and he said, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That means, get going, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Just disappear like-- you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he let us go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But that was in the very beginning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Those things did not happen later on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was there a registration of Jews?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Golly.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not so sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I am not sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
